        <p>Instructions:\n</p>
        <p>
            <ul>
                <li>Time Wave uses proximity sensor to detect activity around the phone.\n</li>
				<li>There are four operations that you can perform. To perform an operation, hover on the proximity sensor (Cover your phone with your hand).\n\n</li>
				
				<li>Toggle Play/Pause - Cover phone for less than 1 sec.\n</li>
				<li>Next - Cover phone for 1 seconds\n</li>
				<li>Previous - Cover phone for two seconds\n</li>
				<li>Stop - Cover phone for three seconds\n</li>
			    
            </ul>
                
        </p>
    </string>
